{"tid":1037031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時講咗大話係會被誤會一世","createTime":"2019-02-25T15:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T16:13:38.000Z","uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf29e192e5f33df4b76ec2b23149d501fcbaee8","tid":1037031,"uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"唉。<br />\n<br />\n話說當年仲係讀大一，我同班中同就間唔中會聚一聚吹水啦。<br />\n<br />\n有一次講到大家最醉個情況係點，我就懶威威咁話我試過blackout到醒咗之後有個男仔喺隔離。<br />\n<br />\n其實我從來無試過飲到咁醉/令自己咁危險囉&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n點知班中同就一唱唱足成世，成日話&ldquo;你飲到blackout,醒咗後有個男仔喺隔離渦&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n唉，我真係覺得自己好on9，做咩講埋啲咁嘅大話令到自己形象永久受損<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91d8938473a96ca8b54d03296a0b3a1d15d590a","tid":1037031,"uid":30578,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:02:58.000Z","msg":"gay post?"},{"pid":"cbed1c6eb927b159fe68dfb6871706b951918e6e","tid":1037031,"uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b91d8938473a96ca8b54d03296a0b3a1d15d590a","tid":1037031,"uid":30578,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:02:58.000Z","msg":"gay post?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:04:12.000Z","msg":"非gay"},{"pid":"c911a735751222bb9fe3998746e4e2a3405c8a14","tid":1037031,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2eb396f368342a7a57b061e1e5b33fe13a166d60","tid":1037031,"uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c911a735751222bb9fe3998746e4e2a3405c8a14","tid":1037031,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"我真係笑到收唔到聲。<br />\n你當年係咪受E神受傷一事而得到啟發？"}]}